cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with a multi-agent output regulation problem, which involves control systems and networked agents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also proposes a distributed controller that uses consensus protocols, which falls under the category of cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The paper leverages methods from internal model based controller synthesis, which is related to cs.LG (Learning). The paper also deals with uncertain agent dynamics, which is related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
